   Message From The Chair
   Elmy Bermejo
   Welcome to the California Commission on the Status of Women's website.
   Here you can find information about the Commission, who the
   Commissioners are, our priority legislation in the legislative cycle,
   other exciting projects and events and much, much more. You will also
   find links to state agencies and other organizations.
   We hope that this will be a useful resource for you and that you will
   encourage others to visit our site. Feel free to contact us by phone or
   email. We look forward to hearing from you.

